  m_Script: {fileID: 11500000, guid: 5f67c7e9798c5184d935fcf3e0f69ebc, type: 3}
  m_Name: TutorialChallenge2.2Intro
  m_EditorClassIdentifier: Assembly-CSharp::DialogueSO
  dialogueLines:
  - Now that your enemy has ended their turn, it's time to fight back.
  - In the middle is your sequencer. Where in you are only allowed three spells.
  - You may order them by dragging them to any other slots.
  - You may also discard and replace them by dragging them outside the sequencer
    and forming a new spell.
  - Form a spell, and click cast once you are done.
